00:19:36,175 --> 00:19:37,968
Wow. Interesting.

400
00:19:38,051 --> 00:19:39,428
-Should I go first?
-Yes.

401
00:19:39,928 --> 00:19:44,141
"I don't talk much
so I come across as cold at first."

402
00:19:44,224 --> 00:19:46,435
"But when I like someone,

403
00:19:46,518 --> 00:19:48,270
I become very affectionate, like a puppy."

404
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:52,941
"I'm competitive, so when I like someone,
I just go full steam."

405
00:19:53,025 --> 00:19:55,986
"I'm attracted to
modest and refined vibes."

406
00:19:56,069 --> 00:19:57,779
"I'm also attracted to people
who are cute and affectionate

407
00:19:57,863 --> 00:19:59,198
because I'm very affectionate myself."

408
00:20:01,575 --> 00:20:03,827
"I want a relationship
where we both feel secure

409
00:20:03,911 --> 00:20:06,413
and plan our future together

410
00:20:06,496 --> 00:20:09,917
because I want to
marry someone before I turn 30."

411
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,293
