412
00:20:11,376 --> 00:20:13,462
ANONYMOUS SUBJECT 1:
PUPPY-LIKE PERSON WHO WANTS TO GET MARRIED

413
00:20:14,463 --> 00:20:16,924
<i>This person came on this show</i>
<i>to get married.</i>

414
00:20:18,550 --> 00:20:19,551
