in an interesting way."

433
00:21:10,435 --> 00:21:13,855
<i>I want to meet someone</i>
<i>who really enjoys their job.</i>

434
00:21:13,939 --> 00:21:17,484
I don't think I've met someone
who enjoys their job

435
00:21:17,567 --> 00:21:18,819
