439
00:21:26,201 --> 00:21:27,661
That's who I want.

440
00:21:30,539 --> 00:21:32,124
"Who am I?"

441
00:21:32,207 --> 00:21:33,709
ANONYMOUS SUBJECT 3:
LOVES MOVIES AND THEIR CAREER

442
00:21:33,792 --> 00:21:36,420
I see you really enjoyed <i>La La Land.</i>

443
00:21:37,004 --> 00:21:37,963
HYUN-JIN: LOVES MOVIES AND HER CAREER

444
00:21:38,046 --> 00:21:38,964
I see.

445
00:21:39,548 --> 00:21:40,424
Puppy-like, right?

446
00:21:40,507 --> 00:21:42,509
No, I'm the side-dishes person.

447
00:21:42,592 --> 00:21:43,677
-Really?
-Yes.

448
00:21:44,761 --> 00:21:46,805
<i>I would make side dishes</i>

449
00:21:46,888 --> 00:21:49,558
like braised anchovies
or soy sauce-braised quail eggs.

450
00:21:50,142 --> 00:21:54,896
I think I did it hoping
that the person I love

451
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:56,857
would eat well and enjoy their meals.

452
00:21:57,482 --> 00:21:59,943
My father was the only one
that took care of us,

453
00:22:00,569 --> 00:22:02,362
and when we got up every morning,

454
00:22:02,446 --> 00:22:05,365
he would have rice, side dishes ready,

455
00:22:05,449 --> 00:22:08,577
<i>and would even leave a letter for us</i>
<i>before he went to work.</i>

456
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:10,287
<i>From those things,</i>

457
00:22:10,787 --> 00:22:15,000
I felt that my father's love
for us was really deep.

458
00:22:15,083 --> 00:22:19,087
The way I show my affection
was influenced by that as well.

459
00:22:19,171 --> 00:22:25,469
I felt like they were
both very gentle and kind.

460
00:22:26,053 --> 00:22:27,179
You're the puppy-like person?

461
00:22:27,721 --> 00:22:28,555
Yes.

462
00:22:28,638 --> 00:22:30,307
-Oh.
-Puppy-like.

463
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:31,558
SI-HYUN:
PUPPY-LIKE PERSON WHO WANTS TO GET MARRIED

464
00:22:31,641 --> 00:22:35,937
If I can, I'd like to
get married before I turn 30.

465
00:22:36,021 --> 00:22:37,689
I think the best thing about marriage is

466
00:22:37,773 --> 00:22:41,485
