478
00:23:10,722 --> 00:23:14,810
If there is someone he likes,
he would actively pursue them.

479
00:23:14,893 --> 00:23:18,522
If we both like the same person,
he's going to get competitive.

480
00:23:19,231 --> 00:23:21,441
