490
00:23:51,471 --> 00:23:53,098
You can tell me when you want to.

491
00:23:58,186 --> 00:23:59,187
Bon appétit.

492
00:23:59,271 --> 00:24:01,189
-Bon appétit.
-Enjoy.

493
00:24:01,857 --> 00:24:03,775
