499
00:24:23,837 --> 00:24:25,463
<i>Thank you for the food.</i>

500
00:24:25,547 --> 00:24:27,424
-Thank you for dinner.
-Thank you for dinner.

501
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:30,302
