so much time on that shot.

504
00:24:37,309 --> 00:24:38,560
How daring!

505
00:24:38,643 --> 00:24:39,936
We just skip that.

506
00:24:40,020 --> 00:24:41,813
-What did they eat?
-I have no idea.

507
00:24:41,897 --> 00:24:44,149
