527
00:25:26,441 --> 00:25:28,735
Two puppy-like people
and two cat-like people.

528
00:25:31,238 --> 00:25:33,573
One cat-like woman
and one puppy-like woman.

529
00:25:33,657 --> 00:25:37,035
One cat-like man
and one puppy-like man. Four in total.

530
00:25:37,118 --> 00:25:38,912
