565
00:27:11,755 --> 00:27:15,050
<i>I'd get into a relationship</i>
<i>with them pretty quickly.</i>

566
00:27:15,133 --> 00:27:18,595
WE DID A SURVEY ON SUBJECT 4'S IDEAL TYPE
ONE WEEK AGO

567
00:27:18,678 --> 00:27:21,389
When I dated someone who really liked me,

568
00:27:21,473 --> 00:27:23,308
