574
00:27:32,817 --> 00:27:34,819
I like someone
who's like the edge of tofu.

575
00:27:35,695 --> 00:27:37,155
What I mean by that is

576
00:27:37,238 --> 00:27:38,907
they're soft like tofu,

577
00:27:38,990 --> 00:27:40,408
but not silky-soft

578
00:27:40,492 --> 00:27:41,951
and have somewhat bold features.

579
00:27:42,035 --> 00:27:44,746
Like the edge of tofu.
That's the vibe I'm into.

580
00:27:44,829 --> 00:27:48,875
I like someone who looks soft
but has sharp features.

581
00:27:48,958 --> 00:27:51,044
What on earth is an edge-of-tofu face?

582
00:27:51,127 --> 00:27:53,880
They have a defined nose and sharp jawline
but look soft like tofu.

583
00:27:53,963 --> 00:27:55,131
That's what an edge-of-tofu face is.

584
00:27:55,215 --> 00:27:56,716
-Do you get it?
-Not at all.

585
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:58,134
-Then, just watch.
-Okay.

586
00:27:58,635 --> 00:28:01,638
My ideal personality type is
someone who isn't sensitive

587
00:28:01,721 --> 00:28:04,349
and is easygoing.
I like someone like that.

588
