00:28:09,062 --> 00:28:10,730
DOES ONE OF THESE TWO FIT YOUR IDEAL TYPE?

591
00:28:10,814 --> 00:28:11,981
Yes.

592
00:28:12,065 --> 00:28:13,024
Him.

593
00:28:13,108 --> 00:28:14,692
SHE CHOSE SI-HYUN AS HER IDEAL TYPE

594
00:28:14,776 --> 00:28:15,610
Him.

