601
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:41,177
HER ONCE-IN-A-MILLENNIUM IDEAL TYPE
IS WALKING TOWARD HER

602
00:28:44,264 --> 00:28:45,724
<i>As soon as I saw him,</i>

603
00:28:46,599 --> 00:28:47,600
