611
00:29:07,162 --> 00:29:08,997
-Will you be okay with your bag?
-Yes, I'm okay.

612
00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:10,790
I'll carry it for you.

613
00:29:11,791 --> 00:29:13,209
What's your name?

614
00:29:14,002 --> 00:29:16,755
-I'm Byeon Ji-young.
-Ji-young, I see.

615
00:29:17,338 --> 00:29:18,631
