616
00:29:18,715 --> 00:29:20,341
-Ahn Si-hyun.
-Ahn Si-hyun?

617
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:21,843
What's in this?

618
00:29:21,926 --> 00:29:23,887
-I got some meat and…
-Meat?

619
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:27,474
-And ingredients for <i>doenjang</i> stew.
-Okay.

620
00:29:27,557 --> 00:29:29,058
We ate without any meat.

621
