Jun-seung said he likes
a kind cat-like person who is fashionable.

629
00:29:46,284 --> 00:29:48,369
Jun-seung's going to
fall hard for Ji-young.

630
00:29:48,453 --> 00:29:50,079
Get all entangled!

631
00:29:50,163 --> 00:29:53,792
-Get all entangled!
-Get all entangled!

632
