644
00:30:22,529 --> 00:30:25,573
-I think you'll adapt in no time.
-Really?

645
00:30:28,993 --> 00:30:32,080
<i>I'd like to ask her why she chose me</i>

646
00:30:32,163 --> 00:30:34,499
