674
00:31:41,441 --> 00:31:42,317
No.

675
00:31:43,776 --> 00:31:45,194
She has a kind cat-like face.

676
00:31:45,278 --> 00:31:46,529
She's my type.

677
00:31:46,613 --> 00:31:48,239
How can this be?

678
00:31:48,323 --> 00:31:50,074
