-Wow.

696
00:32:25,652 --> 00:32:26,819
There are exactly four.

697
00:32:26,903 --> 00:32:28,112
That's it.

698
00:32:28,196 --> 00:32:30,031
There are drinks and snacks.

699
00:32:30,114 --> 00:32:32,408
We actually had <i>doenjang</i> stew earlier.

700
00:32:32,492 --> 00:32:33,326
Really?

701
00:32:33,409 --> 00:32:34,661
-Tomorrow?
-<i>Doenjang</i> stew and…

702
00:32:34,744 --> 00:32:37,747
<i>I didn't know how to act at first.</i>

703
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,457
The others probably didn't notice,

704
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:42,168
