705
00:32:42,251 --> 00:32:44,003
-Women stay on the first floor.
-Really?

706
00:32:44,087 --> 00:32:44,963
Men are on the second floor.

707
00:32:45,046 --> 00:32:46,047
Okay.

708
00:32:46,130 --> 00:32:47,757
I'll make it for you.

709
00:32:47,840 --> 00:32:49,884
-Should I go downstairs?
-Yeah.

710
00:32:49,968 --> 00:32:51,052
-Yes.
-Go downstairs.

711
00:32:52,637 --> 00:32:53,930
This is awesome.

712
00:32:54,013 --> 00:32:56,557
You brought her up out of the blue.

713
00:32:56,641 --> 00:32:58,434
