732
00:33:52,196 --> 00:33:54,574
-May I ask your name?
-I'm Wee Jun-seung.

733
00:33:54,657 --> 00:33:56,200
-Jun-seung?
-Jun-seung.

734
00:33:56,284 --> 00:33:57,368
Jun-seung,

735
00:33:57,452 --> 00:33:59,120
