743
00:34:12,759 --> 00:34:14,469
I kept the conversation short.

744
00:34:15,053 --> 00:34:16,345
Do we have another chair?

745
00:34:16,429 --> 00:34:17,805
-Is that one okay?
-Isn't it

746
00:34:17,889 --> 00:34:19,557
